    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chicken strips</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 6-7 min on each side or until browned all over and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
