      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>brown sugar </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>teriyaki sauce</strong></p>",
