    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>teriyaki sauce</strong> to the chicken and stir to combine</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min further or until the sauce has reduced to a sticky consistency – this is your <strong>chicken teriyaki</strong></p><p>Trim, then finely chop your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
